      <h2>Editorial Independence and Integrity</h2>
      
      <h3>Our Commitment to You</h3>
      <p><strong>Editorial Independence:</strong> Our content is created independently of our affiliate relationships. Compensation does not influence our editorial decisions, recommendations, or the information we provide.</p>

