      <ul>
        <li><strong>Separation of Teams:</strong> Our editorial team operates independently from business development</li>
        <li><strong>Objective Criteria:</strong> We use consistent, objective criteria for evaluations and comparisons</li>
        <li><strong>Multiple Sources:</strong> We research multiple options and don't favor partners in our recommendations</li>
        <li><strong>Reader First:</strong> Our primary goal is providing value to readers, not maximizing commissions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
      
      <p>This disclosure is made in compliance with the Federal Trade Commission's (FTC) guidelines on endorsements and testimonials in advertising (16 CFR Part 255).</p>

      <h3>Key FTC Requirements We Follow</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Clear Disclosure:</strong> We clearly disclose when content may result in compensation</li>
        <li><strong>Proximity:</strong> Disclosures are placed near relevant links and content</li>
        <li><strong>Plain Language:</strong> We use clear, understandable language about our relationships</li>
        <li><strong>Honest Opinions:</strong> Our opinions and recommendations reflect genuine beliefs about products and services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Specific Disclosure Locations</h2>
      
      <p>You may find affiliate disclosures in these locations on our website:</p>
      <ul>
