        <li><strong>Footer Information:</strong> General affiliate disclosure in the site footer</li>
        <li><strong>Calculator Pages:</strong> On tools that may generate leads for partners</li>
        <li><strong>Comparison Tables:</strong> On pages comparing insurance companies or services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
      
